  "text": "Here we did not separate the terms proportional to ξ − 1/6 into β 3 , as we did in the previous publication [CITATION_1] . Indeed, such distinction can be done in case it is necessary, then we shall have an independent β 3 -function. But, at the moment, our main interest is the interface between the UV and IR limits in the Effective Action and there is no need to enter into these details.",
